data.description: Assumable loan! Call for details! Beautiful like-new home with tasteful finishes located in far-West Greeley's Promontory subdivision! Bright and open main level featuring elegant white quartz countertops, newer stainless steel appliances, and the kitchen is wide open to the living room. Tasteful upgrades to fixtures and finishes throughout main and upper levels. Modern floor plan setup featuring bedrooms and laundry on 2nd floor. Lots of potential in the unfinished basement! Fully fenced with 6 foot cedar in the back yard, so the pups are ready to move in. Very new, built in 2021! Don't miss this home, setup your showing today!
